  "texts": [
    "You might see some snow.",
    "In December, New York City averages about 4 to 6 inches of snow.",
    "However, snowfall can vary from year to year.",
    "It's always a good idea to check the forecast close to your travel date for the most current information.",
    "New York City's winter weather can be quite unpredictable due to its coastal location."
